\"font-family: GyrePagellaMathJax_Normal;\\\">𝐡</span><span style=\\\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.978em;\\\"></span></span><span style=\\\"position: absolute; top: -3.814em; left: 0.627em;\\\"><span class=\\\"mrow\\\" id=\\\"MathJax-Span-217\\\"><span class=\\\"mi\\\" id=\\\"MathJax-Span-218\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 70.7%; font-family: GyrePagellaMathJax_Normal;\\\">𝑡</span><span class=\\\"mo\\\" id=\\\"MathJax-Span-219\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 70.7%; font-family: GyrePagellaMathJax_Main;\\\">−</span><span class=\\\"mn\\\" id=\\\"MathJax-Span-220\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 70.7%; font-family: GyrePagellaMathJax_Main;\\\">1</span></span><span style=\\\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.978em;\\\"></span></span></span></span><span class=\\\"mo\\\" id=\\\"MathJax-Span-221\\\" style=\\\"font-family: GyrePagellaMathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.238em;\\\">+</span><span class=\\\"msub\\\" id=\\\"MathJax-Span-222\\\" style=\\\"padding-left: 0.238em;\\\"><span style=\\\"display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.861em; height: 0px;\\\"><span style=\\\"position: absolute; clip: rect(3.043em, 1000.55em, 4.211em, -999.996em); top: -3.97em; left: 0em;\\\"><span class=\\\"mi\\\" id=\\\"MathJax-Span-223\\\" style=\\\"font-family: GyrePagellaMathJax_Normal;\\\">𝐛</span><span style=\\\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.978em;\\\"></span></span><span style=\\\"position: absolute; top: -3.814em; left: 0.627em;\\\"><span class=\\\"mi\\\" id=\\\"MathJax-Span-224\\\" style=\\\"font-size: 70.7%; font-family: GyrePagellaMathJax_Normal;\\\">𝑖</span><span style=\\\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.978em;\\\"></span></span></span></span><span class=\\\"mo\\\" id=\\\"MathJax-Span-225\\\" style=\\\"\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: GyrePagellaMathJax_Size1;\\\">)</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\\\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 5.146em;\\\"></span></span></span><span style=\\\"display: inline-block; overflo