t=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\\\"https://doi.org/10.1002/ctd2.70127\\\" class=\\\"cross-ref\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">CrossRef</a>]</li><li id=\\\"B37-applsci-16-04199\\\" class=\\\"html-xx\\\" data-content=\\\"37.\\\">Hochreiter, S.; Schmidhuber, J. Long short-term memory. <span class=\\\"html-italic\\\">Neural Comput.</span> <b>1997</b>, <span class=\\\"html-italic\\\">9</span>, 1735–1780. [<a href=\\\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Long+short-term+memory&amp;author=Hochreiter,+S.&amp;author=Schmidhuber,+J.&amp;publication_year=1997&amp;journal=Neural+Comput.&amp;volume=9&amp;pages=1735%E2%80%931780&amp;doi=10.1162/neco.1997.9.8.1735\\\" class=\\\"google-scholar\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\\\"https://doi.org/10.1162/neco.1997.9.8.1735\\\" class=\\\"cross-ref\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">CrossRef</a>]</li><li id=\\\"B38-applsci-16-04199\\\" class=\\\"html-xx\\\" data-content=\\\"38.\\\">Qayyum, A.; Mazher, M.; Niederer, S.A. Assessing self-supervised xLSTM-UNet architectures for head and neck tumor segmentation. In <span class=\\\"html-italic\\\">Challenge on Head and Neck Tumor Segmentation for MRI-Guided Applications</span>; Springer: Cham, Switzerland, 2024; pp. 166–178. [<a href=\\\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Assessing+self-supervised+xLSTM-UNet+architectures+for+head+and+neck+tumor+segmentation&amp;author=Qayyum,+A.&amp;author=Mazher,+M.&amp;author=Niederer,+S.A.&amp;publication_year=2024&amp;pages=166%E2%80%93178\\\" class=\\\"google-scholar\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Google Scholar</a>]</li><li id=\\\"B39-applsci-16-04199\\\" class=\\\"html-xx\\\" data-content=\\\"39.\\\">Novikov, A.A.; Major, D.; Wimmer, M.; Lenis, D.; Bühler, K. Deep sequential segmentation of organs in volumetric medical scans. <span class=\\\"html-itali